OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1775592346
OL,3,CFarage says Channel Island governments
OL,4,Chave been 'weak' on French ID scheme
OL,6,FNigel Farage has criticised the French
OL,7,Fday-tripper ID scheme, believing it
OL,8,Fcould be a potential 'backdoor' into
OL,9,Fthe UK.
OL,11,FIt comes as foreign visitors
OL,12,Ftravelling to the Channel Islands
OL,13,Fwithout a visa will now need to pay
OL,14,F#16 for an electronic travel
OL,15,Fauthorisation (ETA) from next month.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1775592346
OL,3,CFarage says Channel Island governments
OL,4,Chave been 'weak' on French ID scheme
OL,6,FThose with a British or Irish
OL,7,Fpassport, or who have another
OL,8,Fimmigration permission, such as a
OL,9,Fvisa, settled status, or leave to
OL,10,Fremain, will not require the digital
OL,11,Fpermit.
OL,13,FFrench visitors on day trips will not
OL,14,Fneed an ETA, with nationals still able
OL,15,Fto enter with the French Identity Card
OL,16,FScheme, allowing travel to the Channel
OL,17,FIslands for 24 hours.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1775592346
OL,3,CFarage says Channel Island governments
OL,4,Chave been 'weak' on French ID scheme
OL,6,FHowever, the Reform UK leader told ITV
OL,7,FNews that he believed nothing was
OL,8,Fstopping someone from coming to Jersey
OL,9,For Guernsey on a French ID and then
OL,10,Ftravelling to the UK without an ETA.
OL,12,F"I'm surprised by the decision, and
OL,13,FI'm a little bit surprised that some
OL,14,Fof the Channel Islands' governments
OL,15,Fhave been rather weak on this," Mr
OL,16,FFarage said.
OL,18,FMore than 5,000 people took advantage
OL,19,Fof the French ID scheme when
OL,20,Ftravelling to Guernsey last year,
OL,21,Fbetween January and May.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1775592346
OL,3,CFarage says Channel Island governments
OL,4,Chave been 'weak' on French ID scheme
OL,6,FAs the Channel Islands are part of the
OL,7,FCommon Travel Area, they must align
OL,8,Fthemselves with the ETA scheme, which
OL,9,Fwas first introduced following the
OL,10,FUK's departure from the European Union.
OL,12,FThe scheme allows for security checks
OL,13,Fon visitors before they enter the
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,16,FThe changes will come into force on 23
OL,17,FApril and will be reviewed annually.
OL,19,FBoth Jersey and Guernsey say they will
OL,20,Fmonitor the French day-tripper scheme
OL,21,Fwith the relevant customs authorities.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
